        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I'm wondering wether I should concentrate on bashing or piercing.  I realize that at higher levels I won't be doing much meleeing, but it would be nice to be able to use whatever weapon happens to be in my hand if I do need to engage in combat.</P><P>What types of weapons are common/good items for necros at higher levels?  Are there more piercing weapons or bashing weapons that will be good for me to use?</P><P> </font></td>
