        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I'd vote for piercing, as there are some nice low-delay piercing weapons available.</P><P>On the blunt end, the Smoldering Brand is 9 / 22, procs a DD at level 1, and is now often available for under 1.5kp. This is an incredible weapon for a low level character, my SK was using it to fight level 12 stuff at level 7.</P><P>After about level 30 you are never going to want to melee again, your defense cap is 145 and you will not enjoy taking the double and quad hits for 120.</P><P></P><P><BR>-- <BR>Life is a zero sum game, the only way to win is not to play.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

