        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">As someone else said , you need to melee to max out your Defense (Offense as well but not much use in the long run) in order to raise your AC.</P><P>Aslo at low/medium levels you will likely be carrying a Stein of Moggok so your choice is really between 1HB and Piercing.</P><P>I ended up maxing both via a Staff of Writhing and a Stiletto of the Bloodclaw.</P><P>At 53 I might melee occassionally in a group for a laugh with my dagger but the odd 13-15 dmg doesn't do much to the mob and anyway at Offense Skill 140 my ATK rating is to small to do anything other than MISS.</P><P>Santin</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
