        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Yeah piercing is the way to go. When/if you do the Visceral Dagger quest you will have the best dagger possible for a Necro apart from ubermob drops ratio and damage wise. Throw on Grim Aura and Vampiric Embrace and you could fight pretty well against really low greens. I have maxed out offence and defense and I had a fight with a kodiak the other day while testing out an Obsidian Shard. I barely took a hit at all and dagger procced about 3 times. I don't waste mana on trash, I stab them to death hehehe.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
